@@TJvComboListBox
<TITLEIMG TJvComboListBox>
JVCLInfo
  GROUP=JVCL.ListsAndTrees.Lists
  FLAG=Component
Summary
  A listbox that displays a combobox overlaying the selected item.
Description
  TJvComboListBox is an ownerdrawn listbox that displays a combobox overlaying the selected item.
  If you assign a TPopupMenu to the DropdownMenu property, the menu is displayed when the user clicks
  on the combobox button. This component inherits from TJvCustomListBox and publishes many of its
  properties and events as well as adding new ones like DropdownMenu, DrawStyle, OnDrawImage and
  OnDrawText.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvComboListBox.AddImage
Summary
  Adds an image to the listbox.
Description
  Use AddImage to add a TPicture to the Items list. AddImage is a helper function that assures that
  the image is copied to an internal TPicture and added to the Items.Objects list.
  You can also call Items.AddObject directly if you prefer.
Parameters
  P - The picture to add. A copy is created internally and added to the Items.Objects list.
Return value
  Returns the index of the item in the Items list.
See Also
  Items

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvComboListBox.AddText
Summary
  Adds a string to the listbox.
Description
  Use AddText to add a string to the Items list. AddText is a helper function and is equivalent to
  calling Items.Add.
Parameters
  S - The string to add.
Return value
  Returns the index of the item in the Items list.
See Also
  Items

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvComboListBox.ButtonWidth
Summary
  Defines the width of the combobox button.
Description
  Use ButtonWidth to set the width of the combobox button in the list. The default width is 26 pixels.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvComboListBox.Delete
Summary
  Deletes an item from the Items list.
Description
  Delete is equivalent to Items.Delete but also makes sure that if the item delted contains a
  TPicture, the picture is freed.
Parameters
  Index - \Index of the item to delete.
See Also
  Items

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvComboListBox.DrawStyle
Summary
  Determines how images are drawn in the listbox.
Description
  Use DrawStyle to specify how images are drawn in the listbox.
See Also
  TJvComboListBoxDrawStyle

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvComboListBox.DropdownMenu
Summary
  Determines the popupmenu to display when the user clicks the combobox button.
Description
  Assign a TPopupMenu to the DropdownMenu to display it when the user clicks the combobox button in
  the listbox.
  DropdownMenu is separate from PopupMenu but can point to the same TPopupMenu if necessary.
See Also
  PopupMenu

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvComboListBox.HotTrackCombo
Summary
  Specifies whether a combobox is highlighted when the mouse passes over it.
Description
  Set HotTrackCombo to true to provide visual feedback about which combobox is under the mouse
  When HotTrackCombo is false, there is no visual feedback when the mouse passes over items of the
  list box.

