@@TJvComboListBox.OnDrawImage
Summary
  Occurs when an image is about to be drawn in the list.
Description
  Write a handler for this event when you want to take specific actions when an image is about to be
  drawn.
Parameters
  Sender      - The component that called the event.
  Index       - The index of the item in the Items list.
  APicture    - The image that is about to be drawn
  R           - The TRect of where the image is to be drawn.
  DefaultDraw - Set this to false to prevent the component to draw the image.
See Also
  TJvComboListBox.OnDrawText

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvComboListBox.OnDrawText
Summary
  Occurs when a string is about to be drawn.
Description
  Write a handler for this event when you want to take specific actions when a string is about to be
  drawn.
Parameters
  Sender      - The component that called the event.
  Index       - The index of the item in the Items list.
  AText       - The text to draw.
  R           - The TRect of where the image is to be drawn.
  DefaultDraw - Set this to false to prevent the component to draw the text.
See Also
  TJvComboListBox.OnDrawImage

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvComboListBox.OnDropDown
Summary
  Occurs when the user tries to open the drop-down list by clicking the arrow at the right of the
  control.
Description
  Write an OnDropDown event handler to conditionally prevent opening of a drop-down list.
Parameters
  Sender    - The component that fired the event.
  Index     - The index of the item in the Items list.
  X         - Horizontal pixel coordinates of the mouse pointer in the client area of the Sender.
  Y         - Vertical pixel coordinates of the mouse pointer in the client area of the Sender.
  AllowDrop - Set to true if the drop-down attempt can proceed and false if the attempt to drop-down
              should be aborted.

